sentence: The Base Salary shall be paid to Executive in twelve (12) equal monthly payments at or about the 1st of each month in the amount of Twenty-Nine Thousand, Six Hundred Sixty-Six Dollars US and Sixty-Seven Cents ($ 29,166.67).
